Mojolicious-Plugin-RoutesAuthDBI


Generate routes from sql-table, make authentication and make restrict access (authorization) to route with users/roles tables. Plugin makes an auth operations throught the plugin L<Mojolicious::Plugin::Authentication> on which is based.
INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make test
	make install


